Package: hdxr
Title: Connect to Humanitarian Data Exchange. Extract Useful Information
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Callum", "Taylor", email = "callum.taylor@glasgow.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Connects to the Humanitarian Data Exchange, using the ckanr package. Downloads information and reformats it to something more useable using jsonlite and dplyr
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
